    <h2 id="aboutourprivacypolicy">About our Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>This policy details how data about you collected on our platform, which is comprised of our websites, services, and applications (together, "NeoScaffold"), is used when interacting with NeoScaffold Inc. (referred to in this policy as "NeoScaffold", "we", "us"). NeoScaffold is an app that allows users to create workflows. If we update this policy, we will revise the date, place notices on NeoScaffold if changes are material, and/or obtain your consent as required by law.</p>
    <h2 id="appprivacy">App Privacy</h2>
    <p>This section summarizes your privacy rights regarding our collection and use of your personal information. By installing and using the NeoScaffold app, you agree to our use of your personal information as summarized below and as described by the remainder of the policy.</p>
    <p>To maximize the benefits of the NeoScaffold app, this notice lists the app's optimal collection practices. You will be able to opt-in or modify collection settings according to your device's privacy settings.</p>
    <h3 id="collectionofyourpersonalinformation">Collection of Your Personal Information</h3>
    <p>Workflow data to provide you with a customized experience.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <p>Access to your device's storage to save and load workflows.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <h3 id="useofyourpersonalinformation">Use of Your Personal Information</h3>
    <p>NeoScaffold provides personalized workflow suggestions based on your usage patterns.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <h3 id="sharingofyourpersonalinformation">Sharing of Your Personal Information</h3>
    <p>Shares information with members of our corporate family to improve workflow creation tools and enhance your experience.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <p>Shares information with service providers under contract who help us operate and improve NeoScaffold.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <p>Shares information with law enforcement or authorized third parties to investigate criminal activity or violations of our User Agreement or Policies.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <h3 id="protectionofyourpersonalinformation">Protection of Your Personal Information</h3>
    <p>Protects your workflow data and personal information using technical and administrative security measures to reduce the risks of loss or misuse.</p>
    <p>Yes, this app does this or requests this.</p>
    <h3 id="protectingyourprivacy">Protecting your privacy</h3>
    <p>We have preventative measures in place to stop unauthorized access or misuse of your workflow data and personal information.</p>
    <p>We do not run ads within the NeoScaffold app.</p>
    <p>We do not provide your workflow data or personal information to third parties for research or marketing.</p>
    <p>We do not engage in cross-marketing or link-referral programs.</p>
    <p>We do not send you unsolicited communications for marketing purposes.</p>
    <p>We do not engage in affiliate marketing.</p>
    <p>Please review privacy policies of any third party integrations you may use with NeoScaffold.</p>
    <h3 id="dataweusetoprovideimproveourservicesandorcombatfraudabuse">Data we use to provide/improve our services and/or combat fraud/abuse:</h3>
    <p>Any data that you provided that interacted, directly or indirectly, with NeoScaffold.</p>
    <p>Data from 3rd parties (e.g. geolocation via IP address)</p>
    <p>Data about your device(s) (e.g. screen size, DOM local storage, plugins).</p>
    <p>Data collected via cookies, web beacons, or other usage based data collection technology</p>
    <p>Payment information such as billing (e.g. credit cards)</p>
    <p>Any identity information that is provided by you, 3rd parties, affiliates, or by public services.</p>
    <h3 id="detailsaboutthedataweuse">Details about the data we use</h3>
    <p>We share your information with third party identity verification services in order to prevent fraud. This allows us to confirm your identity by comparing it against public record and third party databases. These service providers might create derivative data based on your personal information that can be used solely in connection with provision of identity verification and fraud prevention services.</p>
    <p>We may share your information with service providers under contract who help with parts of our business operations such as bill collection, marketing, and technology services. Service providers will use the data in accordance to their own Privacy Policy. Our contracts require these service providers to only use your information in connection with the services they perform for us, and prohibit them from selling your information to anyone else.</p>
    <p>We may share your information with companies or other entities that we plan to merge with or be acquired by. Should such a combination occur, we will require that the new combined entity follow this Privacy Policy with respect to your personal information. You will receive prior notice of any change in applicable policies.</p>
    <p>We may share your information with companies or other entities that purchase NeoScaffold assets pursuant to a court-approved sale under U.S. Bankruptcy law;</p>
    <p>We may share your information with law enforcement, and officials, or other third parties when we are compelled to do so by a subpoena, court order, or similar legal procedure, or when we believe in good faith that the disclosure of personal information is necessary to prevent physical harm or financial loss, to report suspected illegal activity or to investigate violations of our User Agreement or any other applicable policies.</p>
    <h3 id="datasafety">Data Safety</h3>
    <p>We maintain (and require our service providers to maintain) appropriate physical, technical, and administrative safeguards to protect the security, and confidentiality of the personal information you entrust to us.</p>
    <p>We cannot fully guarantee the security and confidentiality of data you transmit to us or receive from us before it reaches us or our affiliates under contract.</p>
    <p>We also cannot fully guarantee the confidentiality of data you provide if it has already been revealed to an unauthorized party. If you think your data is no longer secure you should contact us immediately.</p>
    <h3 id="managingaccess">Managing Access to Your Google Account</h3>
    <p>You can manage access to your Google Account and control which data is shared with NeoScaffold by visiting your Google Account settings.</p>
    <p>For more information on how Google helps you share your data safely, please refer to this <a href="https://safety.google/privacy/data-sharing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Safety Center article</a>.</p>
